author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Wittchen FY Net Profit Rises To 21.9 Mln Zlotys
text:
March 30 (Reuters) - Wittchen SA:
* REPORTED ON THURSDAY FY NET PROFIT OF 21.9 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 20.3 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* FY REVENUE 215.0 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 170.3 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* FY EBITDA 40 MILLION ZLOTYS, UP 33 PERCENT YEAR-ON-YEAR
* FY GROSS MARGIN 55.9 PERCENT VERSUS 56.1 PERCENT YEAR AGO
* ADDED 8 RETAIL STORES IN 2017 TO 88 AT END-YEAR, INCREASING TOTAL GROSS COMMERCIAL SPACE BY 10.4% PERCENT TO 6,891 SQUARE METERS
* PLANS TO INCREASE ITS NETWORK TO 100 STORES AT END-2018
